ringer Publishing Company |location= New York}}\n* {{cite book|last=Grant|first=Sally Grant|title=Edith Cavell, 1865\u20131915|url=https://books.google.com/books?id=9-rtngEACAAJ|year=1995|publisher=Larks Press|isbn=978-0-948400-28-5}}\n* {{cite book|last=Grey|first=Elizabeth|title=Friend Within the Gates: The Story of Nurse Edith Cavell|url=https://books.google.com/books?id=-gXWngEACAAJ|year=1973|publisher=Dell Publishing Company}}\n* {{cite book|last=Hamelecourt|first=Juliette Elkon|title=Edith Cavell, Heroic Nurse|url=https://books.google.com/books?id=D2v-GAAACAAJ|year=1956|publisher=J. Messner}}\n* {{cite book|last=Hill|first=William Thomson|title=The Martyrdom of Nurse Cavell: The Life Story of the Victim of Germany's Most Barbarous Crime : With Illustrations|url=https://archive.org/details/martyrdomofnurse00hill|year=1915|publisher=Hutchinson & Co.|location=London}}\n* {{cite book|last=Hoehling|first=Adolph A|title=A whisper of eternity: the mystery of Edith Cavell|url=https://books.google.com/books?id=IGhqAAAAMAAJ|year=1957|publisher=T. Yoseloff}}\n* {{cite book|last=Johnson|first=Jan|title=The Secret Task of Nurse Cavell: A Story about Edith Cavell|url=https://books.google.com/books?id=pRdPAAAACAAJ|year= 1979|publisher=HarperCollins Publishers|isbn=978-0-03-041661-3}}\n* {{cite book|last=Lasswell|first=Harold Dwight|title=Propaganda Technique in World War One|url=https://books.google.com/books?id=UIrpugAACAAJ|year=1927|publisher=MIT Press (MA)|isbn=978-0-262-62018-5}}\n* {{cite book|last=Leeuw|first=Ad\u00e8le De|title=Edith Cavell; Nurse, Spy, Heroine|url=https://archive.org/details/edithcavellnurse00dele|url-access=registration|year=1968|publisher=Putnam}}\n* {{cite journal|last=Marquis|first=Alice Goldfarb|date=Jul 1978|title=Words as Weapons: Propaganda in Britain and Germany during the First World War|journal=Journal of Contemporary History|publisher=Sage Publications, Ltd.|volume=13|issue=3|pages=467\u201398|doi=10.1177/002200947801300304|jstor=260205}}